          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to retrieve a list of users who are associated with a specific role within a given application. It filters users based on a partial match of their usernames. This procedure is part of a membership system, likely used in applications that implement role-based access control."
        }
